https://github.com/Lawouach/WebSocket-for-Python
http://www.defuze.org/oss/ws4py/docs/
http://www.defuze.org/oss/ws4py/docs/index.html

安装websocket测试框架：
apt-get install python-setuptools
apt-get install libevent-dev
apt-get install python-greenlet python-greenlet-dev
apt-get install python-gevent
apt-get install gunicorn
easy_install gevent-websocket
easy_install ws4py

如果成功安装的话，运行时会有错误，把这两行的If语句注释掉
/usr/local/lib/python2.7/dist-packages/gevent/pywsgi.py
Line 394
